ng> and other development tools. Full game source code available.</li></ul><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>New to Ion Fury?</strong> Get <strong>Ion Fury + Aftershock</strong> for the complete experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Already own Ion Fury?</strong> Pick up <strong>Ion Fury: Aftershock</strong> for a full second campaign plus <strong>Arrange Mode</strong>, a mirror-world remix of the original campaign that integrates Aftershock’s new enemies, items, and weapons while reworking map progression, item placement, and enemy encounters.</p>",
